name: A Pillar of Friendship in a Seething Abyss of Noise
description: This is my HENpals piece for @celad00r ( celadoor.xyz ). You were one of the first people I connected with here on HEN, and your art blew my mind then, and it still blows my mind now. Personally, I don't think I would be making my art the same way without you. Thanks forever for the support and friendship! Here's to many many more amazing pieces by both of us :P (and to us collecting some good ones too :P )
